≈ÚµU<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:691:"Alex completed his Doctor of Clinical Psychology (DClinPsych) at the University of Queensland. He has experience working in the public system, for non government organisations, universities, and in private practice. This has included work with children, adolescents, adults, and older adults with a variety of concerns including depression, anxiety disorders, alcohol and substance use problems, grief and loss, adjustment difficulties, bipolar disorder, schizophrenia, eating issues, personality disorders, autism spectrum disorders, learning disorders, and child behaviour problems. Alex has a specific interest in the treatment of post traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) and complex trauma.";}